---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import AdSlot from "../../../components/AdSlot.astro";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Pricing Experiments - Use Case | PricingNest"
  description="A practical flow for pricing experiments: model price increase impact, estimate break-even churn, and compare annual discount tradeoffs."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Use case: pricing experiments</h1>
    <p>
      Use this flow to model a price increase, estimate break-even churn, and compare annual prepay discounts. It's designed
      for quick sensitivity checks before you run an experiment.
    </p>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <a class="btn primary" href="/saas-pricing/pricing-increase-impact-calculator/">Start with price increase impact</a>
      <a class="btn ghost" href="/saas-pricing/use-cases/">All use cases</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="grid">
    <section class="card col8">
      <h2>Recommended steps</h2>
      <ol class="list">
        <li>
          Model revenue impact and break-even churn:{" "}
          <a href="/saas-pricing/pricing-increase-impact-calculator/">pricing increase impact calculator</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          Convert monthly to annual prepay pricing: <a href="/saas-pricing/annual-discount-calculator/">annual discount calculator</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          If the experiment affects retention, sanity-check churn impact:{" "}
          <a href="/saas-pricing/churn-impact-calculator/">churn impact calculator</a>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 1.25rem;">Notes</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Use ranges (best/base/worst) and segment by plan or customer size.</li>
        <li>Grandfathering or phased rollouts can reduce churn risk during a price increase.</li>
        <li>Annual discounts trade revenue for commitment and cash flow; compare effective monthly rates.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <aside class="card col4">
      <h2>Good for</h2>
      <ul class="list">
        <li>Packaging or price-point changes</li>
        <li>Annual prepay strategy</li>
        <li>Sensitivity checks before rollout</li>
      </ul>
      <AdSlot placement="use_case" containerStyle="margin-top: 1rem;" />
    </aside>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
